        "Product_Description": "From park strolls to grocery store runs, the Jeep Aries 2-Seater Stroller Wagon by Delta Children makes any outing an adventure. Designed with today's families in mind, this versatile stroller wagon incorporates features to encourage autonomy, self-discovery, imaginative play, and sensory development. This convertible wagon offers a range of seating options to accommodate two children—both seats can face forward, both can face backwards, both can face inwards, both can face out in different directions, or you can remove the seats completely and use the wagon to carry all your gear. The built-in footrests make facing outwards comfortable for kids of all ages. The wagon’s removable canopy has roll down mesh screens for ventilation or black out privacy screens for on-the-go naps. Take advantage of the wagon’s expansive storage. The wagon features front and rear storage pockets, zippered storage compartments under the seats, kids snack tray, plus two parent cup holders. Two adjustable leatherette handlebars ensure a comfortable grip for parents of all heights, while the large, puncture-proof tires with suspension provide a smooth ride on any terrain. The wagon’s flat fold makes it easy to store and transport. It’s the perfect all-in-one solution for growing families.Easily modify this wagon by adding your car seat and car seat adapter for flexible seating arrangements (both sold separately):A1970 Adapter for Graco SnugRide (30,35,40), Evenflo Embrace, Evenflo Nurture, Chicco Keyfit 30, Britax B-Safe 35A1971 Adapter for Maxi-Cosi Mico 30, Cybex Cloud Q, Nuna PIPA lite rx, Nuna PIPA lite lx, Nuna PIPA lite r, Nuna PIPA lite, Nuna PIPAA1972 Adapter for UPPAbaby MESAA1973 Adapter for Clek LiingA1974 Adapter for Baby Trend EZ Flex-LocA1986 Adapter for Maxi-Cosi Mico 30, Mico 30 Infant, Mico Luxe, Coral 360",
